headline: S&P 500 Sell-Off: How Reliable Dividend Stocks Like Realty Income Can Offer Peace of Mind
summary: Buy reliable dividend stocks like Realty Income (NYSE: O), NNN REIT (NYSE: NNN), and Federal Realty (NYSE: FRT).  If you focus on that instead of the market's unpredictable ups and downs, you'll avoid the stomach-churning madness that is a typical day on Wall Street.
